The paper deals with approximation algorithms for two well-known optimization problems, GMST and GTSP, in a specific setting of points on an integer grid. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of computer science that deal with algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational geometry (cs.CG), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), graph theory (cs.GT), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as these fields are closely related to the problem at hand.
